          en: "Tape ketan utilizes ragi tape starter containing complex microbial ecosystem for sequential fermentation. Microorganisms in ragi: Rhizopus oryzae (dominant mold, 60-70% of microflora), Endomycopsis burtonii (primary fermenting yeast), Saccharomyces cerevisiae, Candida sp., Hansenula sp., and lactic acid bacteria (Lactobacillus, Pediococcus). Process: 1) Steamed glutinous rice cooled to 30-35°C, mixed with crushed ragi (2-3% w/w), wrapped in banana leaves. 2) Incubation 48-72 hours at 28-32°C. Fermentation stages: Phase 1 (0-24h): R. oryzae mycelium grows, producing amyloglucosidase and α-amylase converting amylopectin starch to glucose (15-25% final concentration). Phase 2 (24-48h): Yeasts metabolize glucose through alcoholic fermentation, producing 4-8% ethanol plus flavor volatiles (esters: ethyl acetate, isoamyl acetate). Phase 3 (48-72h): LAB produce lactic acid (0.3-0.8%), lowering pH to 3.8-4.5, preventing spoilage. Final product: sweet-alcoholic-slightly sour flavor, soft texture, pH 4.0-4.5. Consumed as dessert or ingredient. Storage: refrigeration 5-7 days. Over-fermentation (>96h) increases ethanol to 10-12% with pronounced sour notes.",
          es: "Tape ketan utiliza iniciador ragi tape conteniendo ecosistema microbiano complejo para fermentación secuencial. Microorganismos en ragi: Rhizopus oryzae (moho dominante, 60-70% de microflora), Endomycopsis burtonii (levadura fermentadora primaria), Saccharomyces cerevisiae, Candida sp., Hansenula sp., y bacterias de ácido láctico (Lactobacillus, Pediococcus). Proceso: 1) Arroz glutinoso al vapor enfriado a 30-35°C, mezclado con ragi triturado (2-3% p/p), envuelto en hojas de plátano.",
          de: "Tape Ketan verwendet Ragi-Tape-Starter mit komplexem mikrobiellem Ökosystem für sequentielle Fermentation. Mikroorganismen in Ragi: Rhizopus oryzae (dominanter Schimmel, 60-70% der Mikroflora), Endomycopsis burtonii (primäre fermentierende Hefe), Saccharomyces cerevisiae, Candida sp., Hansenula sp., und Milchsäurebakterien (Lactobacillus, Pediococcus). Prozess: 1) Gedämpfter Klebreis auf 30-35°C abgekühlt, mit zerkleinertem Ragi (2-3% w/w) gemischt, in Bananenblätter gewickelt.",
          nl: "Tape ketan gebruikt ragi tape starter bevattend complex microbieel ecosysteem voor sequentiële fermentatie. Micro-organismen in ragi: Rhizopus oryzae (dominante schimmel, 60-70% van microflora), Endomycopsis burtonii (primaire fermenterende gist), Saccharomyces cerevisiae, Candida sp., Hansenula sp., en melkzuur bacteriën (Lactobacillus, Pediococcus). Proces: 1) Gestoomde kleefrijst gekoeld tot 30-35°C, gemengd met vermalen ragi (2-3% w/w), gewikkeld in banaan bladeren."
